title: As Biden rolls back Trump policies, G-20 allies join in bid to revive Iran nuclear deal
content:
1. As Biden rolls back Trump policies, G-20 allies join in bid to revive Iran nuclear deal  The Washington Post
  2. Biden, other leaders say no easing sanctions until Iran slows its nuclear development  NPR
  3. Biden and European leaders say they're 'convinced' Iran deal can be quickly restored  CNN
  4. Biden, trio of European allies discuss Iran nuclear program  KSL.com
  5. Biden, European leaders urge Iran to resume talks to avoid “dangerous escalation”  Axios
